115
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,600
Serves you right.

116
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,639
What happened today is really strange.

117
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,279
Could it really be the blood fox?

118
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,319
Hu Xiaoyun

119
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:07,040
Weren't you the first to notice all this?

120
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,399
Why don't you tell everyone about it?

121
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:09,519
What exactly happened?

122
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,319
Is there really a blood fox curse?

123
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:16,079
Actually, I'm not really sure.

124
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:18,079
Today is my mother-in-law's death anniversary.

125
00:06:18,439 --> 00:06:20,639
I went to visit her grave with my husband.

126
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,120
Then...

127
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,920
Father, Mother...

128
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,800
Your son and daughter-in-law have not been filial.

129
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:32,439
We couldn't come back to visit your grave.

130
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,680
