132
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,720
What was that sound?

133
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,680
What sound? There's nothing.

134
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,439
Don't get so jumpy.

135
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,120
It's such a sunny day,

136
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,519
