140
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:05,560
What nursery rhyme?

141
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:08,519
Sunny day, rain of blood, foxes.

142
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:10,759
On the fifteenth and the first, a living sacrifice.

143
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:12,639
I'm a little scared.

144
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,079
Why don't we head back first?

145
00:07:14,079 --> 00:07:15,639
Okay, let's go.

146
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:20,800
It's the blood fox.

147
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,120
It must be the blood fox.

148
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,000
A curse.

149
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,759
