157
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:45,360
and wanted to find some excitement in the mountains?

158
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,360
Say that again,

159
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,079
and I'll tear your mouth apart.

160
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,040
You think everyone is like you,

161
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:53,480
lying in bed all day thinking about that stuff.

162
00:07:55,439 --> 00:07:57,120
I was just joking.

163
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,319
Why are you getting mad?

164
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:01,800
Or maybe you weren't with your boss Zhou,

165
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,480
but with that dead guy instead,

166
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,160
and your boss Zhou found out,

167
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,879
so the two of them fought.

168
00:08:08,079 --> 00:08:08,720
Exactly.

169
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:10,240
Stop talking nonsense!

170
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,439
Get out of here!

171
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,399
Out!

172
00:08:12,399 --> 00:08:13,279
You're not welcome in my house.

173
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,720
Go, get out!

174
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,639
