177
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:26,319
Yun'er,

178
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:27,439
what are you talking about?

179
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,839
Tell me, will you?

180
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,639
Don't be shy.

181
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:34,559
How about we find a place where no one else is around?

182
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:35,919
Just the two of us.

183
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,279
Have a proper talk with me.

184
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,240
Talk about that dead person.

185
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,399
Did I ask you?

186
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:44,519
You big guy, swaying around.

187
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:44,879
Squat down.

188
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:47,799
Dead person.

189
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,200
