196
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:58,080
Speak.

197
00:08:58,559 --> 00:09:00,039
Today is my mother's death anniversary.

198
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:01,879
What a coincidence.

199
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,840
